<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=2493&amp;p=12257#p12257"><![CDATA[
The menu is intentionally less transparent than the taskbar to make the text more readable. The default skin will not sacrifice readability for looks. If you want a more customized look you need a third-party skin or make one yourself. It is not that hard.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Thu Apr 17, 2014 10:16 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
